title: Jimmy Responds To AOC!
itunes:title: Jimmy Responds To AOC!
description:
Leaked audio exposes Joe Biden's contempt for the Democratic Party base!

AOC is schooled by the NFL's Justin Jackson of the L.A.Rangers over not fighting for Medicare For All!

Phone calls from Bernie Sanders, Chris Christie, Joe Biden, and Al Pacino!

Featuring Stef Zamorano, Ron Placone, and Mike MacRae!
